{"tid":1715084,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［自救］大家一定守護自己個區！！","createTime":"2019-11-13T04:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T04:08:59.000Z","uid":10630,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2f89df344223e6b6e9c674eb84f2d71457c77204","tid":1715084,"uid":10630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:07:34.000Z","msg":"睇到隔離po話元朗有藍屍岀黎打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然今日好成功癱瘓香港交通<br />\n但都同時 會令到我地都無辦法岀去幫拖<br />\n<br />\n開呢個post係想同大家講<br />\n如果自己個區有咩事 <br />\n一定要齊心去去守護幫手救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係荃灣同元朗人 成日有黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好有分化 一齊努力！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續捱落去 一定會成功！"},{"pid":"fee2fb0b63515f403c3132281144c2eb0c2bd8c0","tid":1715084,"uid":10630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:07:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"11ed2651005127beefb45a9069e72d193951208c","tid":1715084,"uid":10630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:08:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a306f7cfc02b2d142c4c5bbc53c94f896c5a6ddd","tid":1715084,"uid":10630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:08:47.000Z","msg":"自己個區自己救！"},{"pid":"ed1adc4476d0703f8c5763715038ae09cf8be87f","tid":1715084,"uid":10630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:08:59.000Z","msg":"自己個區自己救！"}]}